NOTICE OF ASSESSMENT LIEN
MILLER RANCH ASSOCIATION INC.
File No .: 9175-326-4649
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
WHEREAS, that certain Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Miller Ranch Association Inc. (hereinafter
"Association"), recorded in/under Document # 20050037305 of the Real Property Records of Bexar County, Texas (hereinafter
"Declaration") provides for a lien against the property located at 6339 Fence Crossing, San Antonio, TX 78244 (hereinafter
"Property") for the benefit of the Association to secure the payment of assessments levied against the Property for common
expenses and fees.
WHEREAS, the Declaration provides that the Association is vested with the power to assess, collect assessments, and enforce the
lien retained against the Property.
WHEREAS, according to the Association's records, MUPR 3 ASSETS LLC, (hereinafter "Owner," whether one or more) is the
Owner of the Property legally described as follows:
LOT 23, BLOCK 13, MILLER RANCH SUBDIVISION, UNIT 1, BEXAR COUNTY, TEXAS, ACCORDING TO THE MAP
OR PLAT THEREOF RECORDED IN VOLUME 9564, PAGE(S) 72, DEED AND PLAT RECORDS OF BEXAR COUNTY,
TEXAS.
WHEREAS, Owner is in default in the Owner's obligations to make payments for assessments and has failed, despite demand
upon the Owner, to pay Association assessments, handling charges, and collection costs properly levied against the Property, in
the amount as of 08/23/2021 equal to $624.30, which amount may continue to increase.
NOW THEREFORE, the Association, acting by and through a member of its Board of Directors, its duly authorized agent,
and/or its attorney, does hereby file this Notice of Assessment Lien against the Property due to non-payment of the amounts
contained herein as of the date set forth above.
EXECUTED this 3 day of __ 720
22
LAW OFFICE OF BRADY T. WYATT, III
Drady T. Wyatt, Ing
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF DALLAS

200 by Brady T. Wyatt, III on
behalf of the Law Office of Brady T. Wyatt, III, acting on behalf of Associa Hill Country San Antonio, the duly authorized
agent for Miller Ranch Association Inc.
GRACIELA ITZEL JASSO
Notary Public, State of Texas
Comm. Expires 11-10-2024
Notary ID 130896155
